✅ 1. Perkara Diperlukan
📱 Aplikasi & Platform

Blynk IoT (versi baharu)
Akaun di https://blynk.cloud/

Aplikasi Blynk IoT di Android/iOS
📦 Library
Install: Blynk, DHT, Servo melalui Library Manager

⚠️ Pakej Blynk
Guna Template + Device (bukan legacy token)
Gunakan Blynk Edgent (atau Blynk Simple ESP32) untuk sambungan WiFi

🛠️ 2. Setup di Blynk Cloud
🧱 Langkah Setup di Blynk Dashboard
Log masuk ke https://blynk.cloud/
Klik + New Template
Name: Smart Environment Monitor
Hardware: ESP32
Connection: WiFi
Klik Save

Tambah Data Stream:
Temperature → V0
Humidity → V1
Rain → V2
Gas → V3
WaterLevel → V4
LED Control → V5 (optional Switch)

Create New Device → From Template → Pilih template tadi

Salin:
Template ID
Device Name
Auth Token

4. Susun Atur Widget dalam App Blynk (Mobile)
| **Komponen**      | **Type**    | **Datastream** |
| ----------------- | ----------- | -------------- |
| Temperature       | Gauge       | V0             |
| Humidity          | Gauge       | V1             |
| Rain Sensor       | Value       | V2             |
| Gas Sensor        | Value       | V3             |
| Water Level       | LED / Value | V4             |
| LED Control (opt) | Switch      | V5             |
